supporting trade with <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">China</ENAMEX> ("<ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">The East Is in the Red"</ENAMEX>) by attacking me as a hireling of
protectionist interests directed by textile <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">magnate</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Roger Milliken</ENAMEX>. Since I
neither read his article on <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">China</ENAMEX> nor wrote him a letter, the logic that leads
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Krugman</ENAMEX> to a gratuitous strike at me is unclear.

