<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Milliken</ENAMEX>'s objections, provided critical support to the passage of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">NAFTA</ENAMEX> and
the ratification of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">World Trade Organization</ENAMEX> and free-trade arrangements
concluded in the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Uruguay Round</ENAMEX>. Thus, our support of free trade amounts to more
