<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Roger Milliken</ENAMEX>, I don't always agree with him, but he is an honest and
honorable <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">man</ENAMEX> from whom <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Paul Krugman</ENAMEX> could learn a lot.

