others, amply support my claim that <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">U.S.</ENAMEX> living standards have been declining
in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">the last two decades</TIMEX>, and refute <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Krugman</ENAMEX>'s claim that <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">First</NUMEX>- and Third World
wages are converging "through a process of leveling up, not leveling down." Nor
